headline: Billions Return To US Crypto ETFs As Bitcoin Hits New All-Time High
summary: US-listed Bitcoin and Ethereum ETFs drew over $4.5 billion in net inflows last week, signaling renewed institutional confidence.

headline: Private Equity Is Coming to Your 401(k). Should You Buy In?
summary: With private-equity funds on their way into workplace retirement plans, savers face a choice that matters: Are they worth adding to my portfolio?  The model has generated outsize gains for some investors in the years since the financial crisis, especially institutions like pension funds and high-net-worth individuals.  Now, however, the Trump administration is working on rules that would let retirement plans offer private-equity funds and other “alternative investments” to ordinary investors.

headline: Wall Street, crypto industry say tokenization will reshape global markets: 'It’s going to eat the entire financial system'
summary: The crypto industry, along with Wall Street heavyweights, wants to bring tokenized stocks, or digital versions of traditional shares that are recorded on a blockchain's digital ledger, into the mainstream.

headline: Bitcoin price surges to all-time high above $125,000
summary: Bitcoin's price set an all-time high of $125,700 on October 5, clearing the previous bitcoin price record high from August.
